data.description: Welcome to this charming 2005 2-story home, nestled on a tranquil street offering both convenience and comfort. With 4 thoughtfully placed bedrooms on the upper level, privacy and togetherness seamlessly coexist for your family. Meticulously maintained and tastefully updated, this residence greets you with an open-concept main floor, presenting an adaptable space from kitchen to dining to living area. Highlighting the property is its exterior-an outstanding feature. The Homeowners Association diligently manages landscaping and snow removal, granting you more time to relish life. The expansive lot presents an excellent opportunity for a full fence installation to enhance privacy or accommodate pets. Beyond the property, effortless freeway access streamlines your daily commute. Meanwhile, the tranquil ambiance of the quiet street provides the sanctuary you've been seeking. Imagine your mornings on the porch, embracing the serene surroundings. Ample parking is facilitated by the large driveway, while the absence of a basement translates to increased functional square footage on the upper levels. Tailored as a starter home or an ideal family haven, this residence blends layout and features seamlessly.
